# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# StackRadar — Production .gitignore
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Secrets & Environment ──
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key

# ── Python / Backend ──
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
*.egg
*.egg-info/
.Python
venv/
.venv/
env/
ENV/

# ── Database (runtime) ──
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# ── Logs (runtime) ──
*.log
backend/logs/

# ── Celery (legacy) ──
celerybeat-schedule*

# ── Test / Coverage ──
.coverage
.coverage.*
.pytest_cache/
.hypothesis/
htmlcov/
coverage.xml

# ── Node / Frontend ──
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ── Next.js Build ──
.next/
out/
.swc/
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# ── Generic Build ──
build/
dist/

# ── OS ──
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db

# ── IDE ──
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# ── Project-Specific (generated / scratch) ──
worker_logs.txt
files.txt
